  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AllMacrosLatexCallback
    Callback to download a LaTeX file defining a unique command for each macro of the lab.
    AllPlotsCallback
    Callback to download all plots as a single, multi-page PDF file.
    AllPlotsLatexCallback
    Callback to download a LaTeX file defining a unique command for each plot of the lab.
    AllTablesCallback
    Callback to download all tables as a single LaTeX file.
    AssistantPageCallback
    Callback to display, start and stop the lab assistant.
    CssCallback
    Special callback for the CSS file.
    CustomPageCallback  
    DownloadCallback
    Callback to download the lab's data.
    EditParametersCallback  
    EditParametersFormCallback
    Callback showing a form to edit the parameters of one specific experiment.
    ExperimentPageCallback
    Callback to display the details of one specific experiment.
    ExperimentsPageCallback
    Callback to display the list of experiments in the lab
    ExplainCallback
    Callback producing a provenance tree from one of the lab's data points.
    ExplainImageCallback
    Callback producing an image explaining the provenance of a data point, as an image in various formats.
    ExportStaticCallback
    Exports the whole contents of the lab's web interface as a bundle of static HTML files.
    FindFormCallback
    Callback for to find a data point by its LDI
    HelpPageCallback
    Callback for the help page
    HomePageCallback
    Callback for the home page, showing the lab's description
    HttpUtilities
    Provides a few methods for processing HTTP requests, mostly when they have a binary payload.
    LabPalServer
    Server supporting LabPal's web GUI
    MacrosPageCallback
    Callback showing the list of macros defined in this lab
    MergeCallback
    Merges the current lab with the one sent in the HTTP request
    PlotImageCallback
    Callback producing an image from one of the lab's plots, in various formats.
    PlotsPageCallback
    Callback showing a list of plots
    ReportResultsCallback
    Triggers the sending of experimental data by the results reported associated to the lab.
    StatusPageCallback
    Callback for the home page, showing various statistics and basic data about the current lab.
    TableExportCallback
    Callback producing an table from the lab, in various formats.
    TablePageCallback
    Callback producing a file from one of the lab's tables, in various formats.
    TablesPageCallback
    Callback showing a list of tables
    TemplatePageCallback
    Callback for a template page.
    UnavailableCallback
    Callback for a special page, used only in the static export of a lab, saying that some feature is not available.
    UploadCallback
    Callback for loading a new laboratory from an uploaded file.
    WebCallback
    Callback for an HTTP request in the ParkBench server.
